      "content": "that makes sense. so if i'm writing an essay, how should i frame the critiques of originalism? people say it's basically just a way for conservative judges to get the outcomes they want, so i want to make sure i explain that part right. is there a standard way to argue that it's more of a political tool than a real legal method?",
